*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZGAMZEY_EASY_CHECKBOX
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zgy_easy_checkbox.

PARAMETERS:
  cb1 AS CHECKBOX,
  cb2 AS CHECKBOX,
  cb3 AS CHECKBOX.

DATA: gv_num TYPE i.
gv_num = 10.

IF cb1 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM iki_ekle.
ENDIF.
IF cb2 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM uc_ekle.
ENDIF.
IF cb3 EQ 'X'.
  PERFORM bes_ekle.
ENDIF.


WRITE: gv_num.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form IKI_EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM iki_ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form UC_EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM uc_ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 3.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form BES_EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM bes_ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 5.
ENDFORM.
